This year, the study of the Association of Russian Managers "Top-1000 Russian Managers" is coming out for the 16th time.
As a tool for assessing the professional reputation of Russian managers of the upper echelon, the study summarises the work of Russian managers for a year, identifying leaders in industries and functional areas.
The initial pool of candidates consists of the winners of the ranking last year.
Last year’s winners are invited to confirm their participation as the candidate of the current year’s ranking and to appoint members of their management team.
In addition, each of the candidates included in the original list is proposed to propose up to ten new managers from other companies, which it would be advisable to add to the overall pool of candidates.
